BT /F3 8.5 Tf 64 179 Td (Token[NUMBER "10" 10.0 at line 1]) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 54 155 Td (8. Parser) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 137 Td (The parser receives the token list and checks whether the tokens follow the grammar of ) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 124 Td (the language. It then builds an AST, which stands for Abstract Syntax Tree.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 103 Td (The required parser API is:) Tj ET
BT /F3 8.5 Tf 64 77 Td (public Parser\(List<Token> tokens\)) Tj ET
